      "id": "PopularPost126883",
      "post_content": "The melvin in me is enjoying this card.  \nYou want to choose a higher number early game, just so you can pay his echo the next turn.  \nHe's good spot-removal on some of the biggest baddies, and Johnny can get behind his combo abilities.  \n  \nAll around, an excellent card. I only wish all cards could be so flavorful and dynamic.",
