      "post_content": "@Implied Quotient, you raised a really good point - then made the same mistake. Ivory Mask won't do anything because the Hellion doesn't target you. Similarly Runed Halo won't do anything but try to prevent the damage, which as you point out can't happen.  \n  \nChildren of Korlis is useful; but good luck paying the echo.  \n  \nI think the card doesn't really need a combo to be good; but if you do I recommend [Mogg Fanatic](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mogg Fanatic) to kill an opponent with less life than you.",
