      "id": "PopularPost145122",
      "post_content": "[Thick-Skinned Goblin](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Thick-Skinned Goblin) for the echo cost.  \n  \n@yespls  \nIf something says it can do something, and something else says it can't, you must go with the latter.  \n  \n*615.11. Some effects state that damage \u201ccan\u2019t be prevented.\u201d If unpreventable damage would be dealt,   \nany applicable prevention effects are still applied to it. Those effects won\u2019t prevent any damage, but   \nany additional effects they have will take place. Existing damage prevention shields won\u2019t be   \nreduced by damage that can\u2019t be prevented.*  \n  \nTherefore, Glacial Chasm cannot prevent the damage from Valcano Hellion. Also, this card doesn't target you, it only targets the creature. Therefore, any redirect that states something like, \"Redirect the next spell or ability that would target you\" wouldn't work, e.g. [Willbender](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Willbender) could redirect the damage from Volcano Hellion targeting one creature to another, but it couldn't redirect the damage being dealt to you. Neither could [Spellskite](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Spellskite)... [(see all)](javascript:void(0);)",
      "posted_by": "igniteice",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost145122\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_post\"><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Thick-Skinned Goblin\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Thick-Skinned Goblin\">Thick-Skinned Goblin</a> for the echo cost.<br/><br/>@yespls<br/>If something says it can do something, and something else says it can't, you must go with the latter.<br/><br/><i>615.11. Some effects state that damage \u201ccan\u2019t be prevented.\u201d If unpreventable damage would be dealt, <br/>any applicable prevention effects are still applied to it. Those effects won\u2019t prevent any damage, but <br/>any additional effects they have will take place. Existing damage prevention shields won\u2019t be <br/>reduced by damage that can\u2019t be prevented.</i><br/><br/>Therefore, Glacial Chasm cannot prevent the damage from Valcano Hellion. Also, this card doesn't target you, it only targets the creature. Therefore, any redirect that states something like, \"Redirect the next spell or ability that would target you\" wouldn't work, e.g. <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Willbender\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Willbender\">Willbender</a> could redirect the damage from Volcano Hellion targeting one creature to another, but it couldn't redirect the damage being dealt to you. Neither could <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Spellskite\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Spellskite\">Spellskite</a>... <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" onclick=\"ExpandPost(event, this, 145122)\">(see all)</a></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '145122'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy56965\">igniteice</span>\r\n                                (2/26/2013 12:00:23 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>"
